//Mold Touch
@73566 = ~Wand of Mold Touch~
@73567 = ~Upon activation, this wand infects the creature the wielder touches with a rapidly spreading brown mold. If the infected creature fails a Save vs. Spell, the infection is severe; if the Saving Throw is successful, the damage is reduced.

Each round after the first, the nearest creature within 10 ft. of the victim must make a Save vs. Wand or be infected by the mold at full strength. This process continues until the mold fails to infect a suitable host in time. Creatures already under the effects of the mold cannot contract it again. The brown mold quickly dies once the spell expires.

